    "## Full EMC catalogue \u2014 rocky + temperate planets\n",
    "\n",
    "Stellar params sourced in two tiers:\n",
    "1. **NEA** (`pscomppars.txt`) via `nasa_name` \u2192 `pl_name`: provides `st_teff`, `st_rad`, `st_spectype`, and `pl_insol` (insolation, already in S\u2295).\n",
    "2. **SIMBAD** fallback for EMC-only planets: joins `basic` \u2192 `mesFe_h` on `oidref` using the EMC `main_id` to retrieve `sp_type` and mean Teff. Stellar radius estimated from a ZAMS Teff\u2013radius relation."
   ]
